{"title":"「一本通 1.2 例 2」Best Cow Fences","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/427#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=427","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/427/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/427/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/427"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"**原题来自：USACO 2003 Mar. Green**\r\n\r\n给定一个长度为 $n$ 的非负整数序列 $A$ ，求一个平均数最大的，长度不小于 $L$ 的子段。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行用空格分隔的两个整数 $n$ 和 $L$；\r\n\r\n第二行为 $n$ 个用空格隔开的非负整数，表示 $A_i$。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出一个整数，表示答案的 $1000$ 倍。不用四舍五入，直接输出。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n10 6\r\n6 4 2 10 3 8 5 9 4 1 \r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n6500\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$1 \\leq n \\leq 10^5$, $0 \\leq A_i \\leq 2000$。"}]}